data.description: Bridge City ISD! This would be the perfect rental property located less than 10 minutes from the new Chevron plant in Orange!   Drive into this lovely neighborhood and up to your cozy new home or rental property! With a fabulous patio as you walk up, this home features a great layout that utilizes the square footage perfectly to feel open and spacious. Large entry area to place your entry table or store your things as you come in the home. The living area flows into the kitchen with a nice size laundry room off of the kitchen, with outside access as well. The two spacious bedrooms and bathroom is perfect for all of your needs. The backyard is spacious and seller has recently added a great outdoor fire pit area for all of your guests to gather round in the cooler months!
